    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken super good care of it, and it's been kept sparkling clean inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the full showroom price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Come swing by and take it for a spin; I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love at first sight!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 1997 Acura Integra Type R, a pinnacle of front-wheel-drive engineering. This specimen features the high-compression B18C5 power plant, retaining its factory-spec hand-polished intake ports and 8,400 RPM redline. The close-ratio five-speed transaxle shifts with surgical precision, feeding power through the original helical limited-slip differential. Its seam-welded chassis remains exceptionally rigid, providing the telepathic turn-in response these DC2s are heralded for. Every factory VIN tag is present, and the interior bolsters show zero compression, confirming its meticulously preserved status. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a mechanically pure, unmodified icon in its definitive Championship White finish.",
      "price": 46500.0,
