      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating, showing zero chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of wear, while the original floor mats look untouched. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, documented service history from the local dealership, ensuring every component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. With exceptionally low mileage and a smoke-free, pet-free history, this is quite possibly the finest specimen available on the market today. Ideal for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
